      "text": "wiſſein winnas Rihkeim / un\npahr wiſſu/ kaß tai peederr/ teem\nbuhs to Telti nest / un wiſſus\nwinnas Rihkus / un wiſſeim\nbuhs pee tahs kalpoht / un ap-\nkahrt to Telti fawu Lehgeri ap-\nmeſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ja ta Telts prohjam\nzelſees / tad buhs teem Lewiteim\nto no-ahrdiht / un kad ta Telts\nſtahwehs / tad buhs teem Lewi-\nteem to uhszelt/un ja tahds Swe-\nfhineks pee-eet tam buhs mirt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un teem Israëta Behr-\nneem buhs ikweenam pee fawa\nLehgera palikt / un ikweenam pee\nfawa Karroga/ pehz faweem Pul-\nkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet teem Lewiteem buhs\napkahrt to Leezibas Dshwokli/ to\nLehgeri apmeſt/ ka ne kahda Duf-\nmiba pahr to Israëta Behrnu\nDraudsi nahk / tapehz buhs teem\nLewiteem to Leezibas Dshwokli\nſargaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad darrija tee Israëta\nBehrni pehz wiſſu/ fo tas KuNgs\nMohsum bij pawehlejis / ta dar-\nrija tee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta II. Nodalla.\nDeetwa Eikums/ ka teem diwpadeſmits Israëla\nZiltim buhs apkahrt to Sa-eeschanas Telti to\nLehgeri apmeſt / un atkah zeltees: 9 / 16/24/3 I.\nJuhda Lehgeris prett Rihteem : 3. Ruhe-\nna Lehgeris prett Deenas-Widdu : 10. Tee\nLewiti ar to Sa-eeschanas Telti paſchā Wid-\ndu : 17. Eewräims prett Wakkaru : 18.\nDans prett Seemeta puſſi : 25.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tas KuNGS runna-\nja us Mohsu/ un us Aä-\nronu/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem Israëka Behrneem\nbuhs to Lehgeri apmeſt/ ikweenam\nappakſch tawu Karrogu / pehz\ntahm Sihmehin fawu Tehwu\nNamma/ tai Sa-eeschanas Telti\npretti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Prett Rihta puſſes / buhs\nteem Juhda Lehgera Karrogeem/\npehz faweem Pulkeem apmeſtes/\nun Naëſſonam / Amminadaba\nDehlam buhs Juhda Behrneem\npar Wirſneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks un win-\nna Pulki bija feptindeſmits\ntſchetr tuhkſtochi/ un fechtints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un klaht winnu buhs tat\nIhsafchara Zilti toLehgert apmeſt/\nun Netaneelam/Zuara Dehlam/\nbuhs teem Ihsafchara Behrneem\npar Wirſneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks un win-\nna Pulki bija peeždefinitis tſchetr\ntuhkfstoſchi / un tſchetrjints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un klaht to Zilti/Sebulans;\nun Gellabam / Gelona Dehlam\nbuhs teem Sebulana Behrneem\npar Wirſneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks un win-\nna Pulki bija peeždefinitis feptin\ntuhkfstoſchi/ un tſchetrſints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pulki ta Juhda Leh-\ngera bija ſintis/ aſtondefinitis un\nfeſch tuhkſtoſchi / un tſchetrſints/\npehz faweem Pulkeem/ teem (faż-\nzija Deews/) buhs papreekſhu\nzeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam Karrogam ta Ruḥ-\nbena Lehgera buhs prett Deenus-\nWiddus puſſi turretees pehz fa-\nweem Pulkeem/ un Eeleazaram/\nZede-\n"
    }
  ],
